#  (2024-04-24)


### Bug Fixes

* Adjust for spaces in nuget path (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/024ecf795d1b2fe66eb9f369b6deddccce0e8663)
* Adjust support for custom target frameworks (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/e7dac5fb84dfc1ebd6be34684f114a624f738e71)
* Adjust task version rename (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/7d31b4ba95a3517fc8094f68087c7de3b13d5872)
* Disable service worker in debug to work around service workers interfering with browserlink (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/160fe912f487b3d6b908480548e980d4d5a60a41)
* Don't define caps when the uno.sdk is present (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/50a2566fec6c16d2ba75fd5fb64864e27c4d3964)
* Ensure that is included Microsoft.NET.ILLink.Tasks in 8.0.200 and later (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/2c93c4911c5a8f7de38ca1cee75a04751bdd6baf)
* More tuner fix for space in nuget path (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/2c60268304d2b929fc6152899fdc3a812cea6ef2)
* remove double slash in path (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/bdbce1c0fe4cf4bff226f342cedf90c3a7d85e43)
* Remove readonly attribute for output path deletion (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/1af64bb5db04b3e96e7bbb8c61ddc28d04abd904)
* Restore clean target (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/45370f2dc5431a8fb865c15cc94dfd886061a424)
* Specify root mode for root assembly (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/0480ecefc64d68dc3d3713f6ed80cea3cc949a44)
* Update runtime to latest (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/0bc4cba23cfbd4452dd047fd4e22ca7179de4ebd)


### Performance Improvements

* Fully disable prefetching (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/ab87a75053554151f1e73dc210032e9ee14814f5)
